[color=#cc0000][size=4]⚠️ [b][u]Heads up[/u][/b][/size][/color]
This page now hosts the [b]Chrome & Blood Modlist Settings[/b] only.

[color=#5cbdcf][size=5][b][u]What is Chrome & Blood?[/u][/b][/size][/color]
[b]Chrome & Blood[/b] is a full overhaul of [i]Cyberpunk 2077[/i] for players who want a faster, harder, and more rewarding Night City. Combat, AI, economy, hacking, cyberware, and stealth have all been reworked. 500+ mods, two profiles, tuned for [b]Very Hard[/b].

Full breakdown, screenshots, the mod list, and setup all live on the [url=https://qcargile.github.io/Chrome-Blood/][b]official website[/b][/url].

[color=#5cbdcf][size=4][b][u]Install[/u][/b][/size][/color]
[list]
[*][b]Recommended:[/b] open the [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/games/cyberpunk2077/collections/lrcdrr]Nexus Collection[/url] and hit [b]Add to Wabbajack[/b].[/*]
[*]Or follow the full [url=https://qcargile.github.io/Chrome-Blood/install.html]install guide[/url] on the website.[/*]
[/list]

[color=#5cbdcf][size=4][b][u]Requirements[/u][/b][/size][/color]
[list]
[*]Official [b]Cyberpunk 2077[/b] + [b]Phantom Liberty DLC[/b], updated to the latest Steam version[/*]
[*][b]SSD required[/b] · [b]Windows 10/11[/b] only[/*]
[*]~12 GB total free space for the list itself[/*]
[/list]

